<p>I ended up buying the same KVM switch I had before, a newer model (the one I had was discontinued). Better KVMs are $200 and up and meant for two screens, which I don&rsquo;t have, so it&rsquo;s a waste. Besides, the performance of the old one was OK.  Meanwhile, I&rsquo;m using <a href="https://github.com/deskflow/deskflow">Deskflow</a>.</p>
